column5: If your gonna be at the Spring Fishing Show on Saturday and ya want an OFC hat to sport around, I just got a box full in that I'm willing to part with for $10 each, shipping and taxes included.  It would be great to see OFC'rs showing off!!v  Plus it would be easy to see who to avoid!!  Gimme a call at 705 753 2387 if ya wanna order one so I can  (well Monique can) mail them out right away!!
Can I grab one at the show?
Put one aside for me please.pm sent
Is there any chance of getting them at the show??  Or do we mail you the cash, cheque.  If its a mail option could you PM me the address, would love to get my hands on one.
Ill have a bunch at the show, but Ill only be there Saturday.. If ya want them at the show, then ill have them at the show!!
Hey TJ, can you bring some stickers that I can buy to put on my boat as well. I will take a hat on saturday as well. I will come see you. Thanks

Thanks Tj, your the best.Tight lines and good fishin to ya always.And Dave too, of course.Vince Team 1 RIPPIN'WEEDS. Watch out for COOLIO the BASSBUGGER.He will flip you a 180 and knock you out.Look out
Ill bring a box of stuff downnn
